    Direct Known Subclasses:
    CompositeActionFly, CompositeActionFlyCatch

    public class CompositeAction
extends UpdatePropagator
implements IAction
    Represents a composite IAction. Contrary to AtomicActions, composite IActions comprise multiple subactions. These subactions can be atomic, but do not have to be.

      • isValidOn

        public boolean isValidOn(IReadOnlyBoard board,
                         Player currentPlayer)
        Returns true if this IAction is valid on the given IBoard and for the given Player, false otherwise. CompositeActions are valid iff their subactions are valid when executed sequentially.
        Specified by:
